packages tree. Notable runtime dependencies:

  Flask, Werkzeug, Jinja2, itsdangerous, click
    License: BSD-3-Clause
    Use:     Web UI / REST control plane.

  pysctp
    License: LGPL-2.1-or-later
    Source:  https://github.com/p1sec/pysctp
