    Use:     NAS / 5G AKA / IPsec primitives.

  scapy
    License: GPL-2.0
    Use:     Packet crafting in select tests.

  iperf3 (system binary, vendored under libs/)
    License: BSD-3-Clause
    Source:  https://github.com/esnet/iperf
